Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people equate drinking\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with having a good time.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But at Proverbs 23:32,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the Bible says that alcohol\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,can ‘bite like a snake.’\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.27,0:00:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there laws\Non drinking alcohol where you live?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, you could be fined,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,be sentenced to community service,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,lose your freedom to drive,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or even go to jail.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if none of those things happen,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,alcohol can lower your inhibitions\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,—and not in a good way.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the influence,\Nyou could say or do things\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you’ll later regret.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if you’re at a party\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and unexpectedly find\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that some are drinking\Nand heading for trouble?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bible says that an intelligent person\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,sees trouble coming and avoids it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop and think.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What might happen if you stay?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you leave before trouble comes\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,without inviting ridicule?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here’s a tip:\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a plan with your parents\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to call or text if you need to leave early.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do\Nif someone pressures you to drink?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At Romans 6:16, the Bible indicates\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that when you let others \Ncontrol your decisions, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you become their slave.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You could just follow along\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and let your peers rule your life.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you could give a firm response\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,—perhaps something like,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,“No thanks!” or “Sorry, I’m not into that!”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you’re out with friends\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and realize the driver has been drinking?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the Bible,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who spends time with fools\N“will fare badly.”\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What could happen\Nif you let that person drive you home?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What other options do you have?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Try this:\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid situations\Nwhere you’ll be with a driver\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,who has a reputation\Nfor drinking and driving.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Always have a Plan B for transportation.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, you don’t have to drink\Nto have a good time,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don’t have to associate with people\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,who think that you do.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the courage to think past the drink.\N
